<DocsLayout
  title="Quick Start"
  description="Get up and running in under 5 minutes with this quick start guide."
  headings={headings}
>
  <h2 id="create-project">Create Your Project</h2>
  <p>Run the following command to create a new project:</p>
  <pre><code>npm create my-app@latest</code></pre>

  <p>You'll be prompted to choose:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Project name</li>
    <li>Template (starter, blog, docs)</li>
    <li>TypeScript support (recommended)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="start-development">Start Development</h2>
  <p>Navigate to your project and start the development server:</p>
  <pre><code>cd my-app
npm run dev</code></pre>

  <p>Your site is now running at <code>http://localhost:4321</code></p>

  <blockquote>
    The development server includes hot module replacement, so changes appear instantly.
  </blockquote>

  <h2 id="build-first-page">Build Your First Page</h2>
  <p>Create a new page by adding a file to the <code>src/pages</code> directory:</p>
  <pre><code>// src/pages/about.astro
---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

&lt;Layout title="About"&gt;
  &lt;h1&gt;About Us&lt;/h1&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;Welcome to our site!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/Layout&gt;</code></pre>

  <p>This page is now accessible at <code>/about</code>.</p>

  <h2 id="add-components">Add Components</h2>
  <p>Create reusable components in the <code>src/components</code> directory:</p>
  <pre><code>// src/components/Card.astro
---
interface Props &#123;
  title: string;
  description: string;
&#125;

const &#123; title, description &#125; = Astro.props;
---

&lt;div class="card"&gt;
  &lt;h3&gt;&#123;title&#125;&lt;/h3&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;&#123;description&#125;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;style&gt;
  .card &#123;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid #eee;
    border-radius: 8px;
  &#125;
&lt;/style&gt;</code></pre>

  <h2 id="deploy">Deploy</h2>
  <p>Build your site for production:</p>
  <pre><code>npm run build</code></pre>

  <p>Deploy the <code>dist</code> folder to any static hosting provider:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Vercel</li>
    <li>Netlify</li>
    <li>Cloudflare Pages</li>
    <li>GitHub Pages</li>
  </ul>
</DocsLayout>
